config AMD_TMRCTR
	bool "AMD AXI Timer"
	help
	  This module implements a kernel device driver for the AXI Timer IP.
	  AXI timer is not capable of matching against a preloaded value.
	  Thus, it's not capable of providing TICKLESS_KERNEL.
